{"data":[{"author":"Ron64","capabilities":[],"category_id":"5261a8fb3b773043d5000012","category_name":"Games","category_color":"b57ad3","changelog":[{"version":"1.0","published_date":"2015-10-19T13:28:04.663Z","release_notes":"1.00 Mastermind Initial release"}],"companions":{"ios":null,"android":null},"compatibility":{"ios":{"supported":true,"min_js_version":-1},"android":{"supported":true},"aplite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":2}},"basalt":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"chalk":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"diorite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"emery":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}}},"created_at":"2015-10-19T12:57:28.620Z","description":"Mastermind is a classic puzzle game. \r\nGuess the sequence, get your hit/miss score and make a better guess, until you find the correct code.\r\nIf you can't find it in 6 rounds, the solution will be displayed.\r\n\r\nIf many users like the game, I will start the multiplayer project, so you can play against other pebble users.\r\n\r\nKeys:\r\nDown- change to next shape(Right)\r\nUp- move to update another shape\r\nSelect- Get hit/miss score for the current combination. (at end, start a new game\r\nBack- Move back to previous shape. Exit if in Left-most shape(or after win/lose)\r\n\r\nFuture plans:\r\n- Let user select colors/shapes\r\n- Count Won/lost\r\n- Add bulls and cows version (numbers 0-9)\r\n- Multiplayer game\r\n- Select shapes using voice\r\n\r\nI'm open to user suggestions. I will add features according to what more users are interested in.","developer_id":"52cf94eff726c8d1d5000038","header_images":"","hearts":18,"icon_image":{"28x28":"https://assets.getpebble.com/api/file/HTLyEt7aRsGYR9PIjsq5/convert?cache=true&fit=crop&w=28&h=28","48x48":"https://assets.getpebble.com/api/file/HTLyEt7aRsGYR9PIjsq5/convert?cache=true&fit=crop&w=48&h=48"},"id":"5624e8b8a0334fce3a00004b","latest_release":{"id":"5624e8eba7d78c82ce00004b","js_version":-1,"pbw_file":"https://www.filepi